1
00:01:35,628 --> 00:01:36,821
Faster!

2
00:01:41,861 --> 00:01:42,849
Give me a bag.

3
00:01:50,095 --> 00:01:51,083
Big Brother.

4
00:02:25,661 --> 00:02:28,456
The real thing,
so it's lived up its name.

5
00:02:28,561 --> 00:02:30,857
Heroine can be had in any quantity.

6
00:02:31,028 --> 00:02:36,120
They say you've a way in NY.
Let's combine

7
00:02:36,262 --> 00:02:37,955
to snatch your heroine businesses
from them.

8
00:02:38,061 --> 00:02:40,357
Okay, it's mutually beneficial.

9
00:02:41,095 --> 00:02:42,993
Now I want 20 kilos of that stuff.

10
00:02:43,162 --> 00:02:44,059
Where's the money?

11
00:02:48,495 --> 00:02:49,585
Here.

12
00:02:51,195 --> 00:02:52,888
Mind you.

13
00:02:53,495 --> 00:02:55,892
Don't talk nonsense
in front of Mr. Big Brother.

14
00:02:57,195 --> 00:03:00,093
Trying to draw?
Are you looking for hell?

15
00:03:00,761 --> 00:03:01,852
Great!

16
00:03:02,228 --> 00:03:05,819
If you work with me,
the other families will go bust.

17
00:03:06,462 --> 00:03:09,053
He's my brother.
Get 20 kgs of stuff for him.

18
00:03:19,128 --> 00:03:20,321
You bustard Ping!

19
00:03:26,095 --> 00:03:27,186
Don't move, CID!

20
00:03:27,228 --> 00:03:28,125
Don't move!

21
00:03:57,961 --> 00:03:59,450
Don't move! Police, drop your gun!

22
00:03:59,629 --> 00:04:00,617
Damn it!

23
00:04:00,762 --> 00:04:02,057
Drop your gun!

24
00:04:20,328 --> 00:04:22,817
Big brother, run!

25
00:04:42,862 --> 00:04:43,953
Stay where you are!

26
00:04:45,796 --> 00:04:49,194
Drop your gun and climb up slowly.

27
00:04:50,662 --> 00:04:54,560
No monkey business! My gun has no eyes.

28
00:04:55,495 --> 00:04:57,893
Put your hands on your ears!

29
00:05:00,096 --> 00:05:02,789
I never flop in any mission!

30
00:05:04,962 --> 00:05:06,053
Damn you!

31
00:05:19,896 --> 00:05:21,089
Are you alright, Uncle Te?

32
00:05:21,263 --> 00:05:22,455
Yes.

33
00:05:23,629 --> 00:05:25,027
Well, an experienced fireman
gets his fingers hurt?

34
00:05:25,428 --> 00:05:26,326
Nonsense!

35
00:06:04,662 --> 00:06:05,650
Trying to run?

36
00:06:06,463 --> 00:06:07,360
Get out of my way!

37
00:06:27,062 --> 00:06:28,153
Stop, police.

38
00:06:37,263 --> 00:06:38,251
Freeze!

39
00:06:49,229 --> 00:06:50,320
Keep away!

40
00:06:50,696 --> 00:06:53,491
Drop your gun! Drop or I'll kill her!

41
00:06:54,263 --> 00:06:56,354
Come on, put it down! Hear me?

42
00:06:56,897 --> 00:06:59,294
Drop it or I'll shoot her dead.

43
00:07:01,463 --> 00:07:02,360
Drop it!

44
00:07:04,062 --> 00:07:05,756
Outrageous! You scum.

45
00:07:34,396 --> 00:07:36,090
Are you sick of living?

46
00:08:08,997 --> 00:08:10,293
Keep down, police!

47
00:08:27,863 --> 00:08:29,658
Are you fed up with living?

48
00:08:33,364 --> 00:08:34,159
After him!

49
00:08:56,763 --> 00:08:58,354
Shirley, don't come up! It's dangerous!

50
00:09:29,897 --> 00:09:30,885
Get the frogmen to salvage.

51
00:09:31,063 --> 00:09:31,858
Yes, sir!

52
00:09:33,364 --> 00:09:34,557
Did you mean to get killed?

53
00:09:39,430 --> 00:09:40,521
Sorry!

54
00:09:55,597 --> 00:09:56,585
Mr. Huang

55
00:09:56,963 --> 00:09:58,554
Cordon off the spot
and call an ambulance.

56
00:09:58,664 --> 00:09:59,459
Yes, sir!

57
00:10:05,097 --> 00:10:06,290
Mr. Huang...

58
00:10:06,397 --> 00:10:07,590
Thank you all for the trouble.

59
00:10:08,364 --> 00:10:11,353
I nearly forgot
to get back a bait for Shirley.

60
00:10:14,330 --> 00:10:15,819
Uncle Te, see how much our haul is,

61
00:10:16,031 --> 00:10:16,928
Yes, sir.

62
00:10:18,197 --> 00:10:21,686
Hsiu, here you are, fixed.

63
00:10:21,831 --> 00:10:22,626
Good.

64
00:10:31,297 --> 00:10:32,285
Mr. Wei.

65
00:10:32,631 --> 00:10:34,120
Here's a file from the USA.

66
00:10:38,831 --> 00:10:40,524
This new drug syndicate

67
