is now in HK.

68
00:10:41,664 --> 00:10:42,755
Watch their movements.

69
00:10:44,364 --> 00:10:45,455
Let's have more.

70
00:10:45,631 --> 00:10:46,824
I've had enough.

71
00:10:46,898 --> 00:10:47,989
Cheers!

72
00:10:48,165 --> 00:10:49,960
Don't...
What?

73
00:10:50,098 --> 00:10:51,290
Really can't drink.

74
00:10:51,397 --> 00:10:53,590
You're lying.

75
00:10:53,731 --> 00:10:54,628
Enough...

76
00:10:55,597 --> 00:10:56,893
Well, I'll drink more tomorrow.

77
00:10:57,031 --> 00:10:57,928
Let's talk about it tomorrow.

78
00:10:58,297 --> 00:10:59,388
Listen,

79
00:10:59,464 --> 00:11:02,056
anyone making trouble tomorrow
will be transferred to Shataukok.

80
00:11:02,330 --> 00:11:03,921
Are you trying to avenge
a personal grudge.

81
00:11:04,064 --> 00:11:05,257
What do you mean?

82
00:11:05,331 --> 00:11:07,421
Mr. Huang judge for us.

83
00:11:07,564 --> 00:11:09,655
We celebrated for him
because we took him for a friend.

84
00:11:09,798 --> 00:11:12,491
He's not taking us for friends.
What do you think?

85
00:11:13,064 --> 00:11:15,053
Help me, or I'll get drunk for sure.

86
00:11:15,165 --> 00:11:16,153
Okay.

87
00:11:17,265 --> 00:11:21,754
You're getting married tomorrow.
Drink this,

88
00:11:22,398 --> 00:11:23,693
