89
00:11:23,864 --> 00:11:25,262
Right, Shirley will stay
to clear up the rubbish.

90
00:11:25,365 --> 00:11:26,762
Don't think it's easy to be a housewife.

91
00:11:26,898 --> 00:11:29,194
Do you want him to drink. I don't.

92
00:11:29,898 --> 00:11:31,387
Well?
Drink it.

93
00:11:32,398 --> 00:11:33,693
Don't drink.

94
00:11:33,831 --> 00:11:35,320
Drink this big glass.

95
00:11:35,465 --> 00:11:38,363
Don't side with him so soon.

96
00:11:40,964 --> 00:11:42,453
We bachelors...

97
00:11:42,597 --> 00:11:44,393
really envy your true feeling.

98
00:11:45,331 --> 00:11:48,229
You're lucky, you're quitting tomorrow.

99
00:11:48,298 --> 00:11:49,593
But we really are depressed.

100
00:11:49,697 --> 00:11:53,289
Why fight? Only yesterday
the doctor said my heart's weak.

101
00:11:53,465 --> 00:11:54,260
What?

102
00:11:54,365 --> 00:11:55,353
I can't stand the shock.

103
00:11:55,498 --> 00:11:57,690
Sometimes you can't take
a doctor advice too serious.

104
00:11:57,764 --> 00:12:00,560
Sister, he can't stand the shock.
Can you?

105
00:12:00,697 --> 00:12:03,788
You don't drink this,
you must clean the house.

106
00:12:03,898 --> 00:12:05,091
Go and collect the ashes.

107
00:12:06,231 --> 00:12:09,322
Drinking's bad for health.
What about venting our feeling?

108
00:12:09,465 --> 00:12:11,363
That suits me better. I'm a virgin.

109
00:12:11,498 --> 00:12:13,396
I've lots of grievances, lets vent them.

110
00:12:14,331 --> 00:12:15,319
Ah Yu, come here!

111
00:12:15,431 --> 00:12:17,329
What's it, Hsiu?
What's wrong with you?

112
00:12:17,465 --> 00:12:18,453
Fix him for me.

113
00:12:18,598 --> 00:12:20,587
Is that an order or a friendly request?

114
00:12:20,732 --> 00:12:22,924
Only a friend would tell you to do this.

115
00:12:23,098 --> 00:12:24,291
Yes, sir.

116
00:12:25,165 --> 00:12:28,256
No peeping and no moving
of lowerjaws.

117
00:12:28,365 --> 00:12:30,160
Anyone blowing the egg
to an opponent win.

118
00:12:37,131 --> 00:12:38,324
Ready?

119
00:12:39,231 --> 00:12:40,322
Ready?

120
00:12:43,031 --> 00:12:44,122
Start!

121
00:13:00,998 --> 00:13:02,692
Hsiu, I'm on your side. Why tease me?

122
00:13:02,799 --> 00:13:05,094
Either we play today or never.

123
00:13:05,165 --> 00:13:08,962
Even if you were my master,
I'd tease you.

124
00:13:09,231 --> 00:13:10,925
Amy...

125
00:13:14,265 --> 00:13:15,458
Terrific!

126
00:13:16,098 --> 00:13:17,189
Make fun of me?

127
00:13:17,231 --> 00:13:20,027
Stop that. Amy really is coming.

128
00:13:20,165 --> 00:13:21,859
I don't care about her.
She really is coming.

129
00:13:21,965 --> 00:13:22,760
So what?

130
00:13:22,899 --> 00:13:23,990
It's you who don't care about me.

131
00:13:25,832 --> 00:13:26,820
Everything alright?

132
00:13:26,965 --> 00:13:28,157
Amy.
What?

133
00:13:29,832 --> 00:13:31,128
How dare you lay hands on my girl?

134
00:13:31,231 --> 00:13:33,027
Protect me.
Stop fooling around.

135
00:13:33,132 --> 00:13:34,529
Forget it!

136
00:13:35,431 --> 00:13:36,522
Outrageous!

137
00:13:38,565 --> 00:13:39,553
Bastard!

138
00:13:39,698 --> 00:13:41,187
How dare you?

139
00:13:41,365 --> 00:13:43,059
Anyone teasing Amy will get it.

140
00:13:43,565 --> 00:13:45,258
He's flaring up.

141
00:13:45,365 --> 00:13:46,353
What's the matter with you?

142
00:13:46,465 --> 00:13:47,362
It's alright.

143
00:13:47,498 --> 00:13:49,589
They're always so wild.
Never mind them.

144
00:13:58,498 --> 00:13:59,395
Mr. Huang, stop him.

145
00:13:59,498 --> 00:14:00,589
What's you up to again?

146
00:14:00,698 --> 00:14:01,595
That bastard hit me.

147
00:14:01,632 --> 00:14:02,825
Don't go so wild, will you?

148
00:14:03,299 --> 00:14:04,696
Mr. Huang, now is the Happy Hour.

149
00:14:04,832 --> 00:14:06,923
We'll go on even if Madam
ordered us to stop.

150
00:14:12,232 --> 00:14:13,925
Dare you even to tease me?

151
00:14:13,999 --> 00:14:14,794
Sorry, sir.

152
00:14:14,932 --> 00:14:16,023
We'll go down to accompany you.

153
00:14:16,999 --> 00:14:19,397
Good, you dared to fling me down.

154
00:14:48,299 --> 00:14:49,196
Come in!

155
00:14:49,366 --> 00:14:50,457
It really got into my head.

156
00:14:59,032 --> 00:15:00,521
Get me a cup of coffee, will you?

157
00:15:00,865 --> 00:15:02,058
Thank you.

158
00:15:04,132 --> 00:15:05,530
For me?

159
00:15:06,666 --> 00:15:09,461
I planned to give it to Shirley.

160
00:15:10,599 --> 00:15:12,588
Now I think it suits you better.

161
00:15:12,732 --> 00:15:14,028
It depends.

162
00:15:17,599 --> 00:15:19,394
How could it suit me?

163
00:15:19,533 --> 00:15:22,328
Not for tonight.

164
00:15:22,466 --> 00:15:25,159
As of tomorrow,
you need to love Shirley.

165
00:15:25,266 --> 00:15:26,254
You're to work like a slave.

166
00:15:30,366 --> 00:15:31,764
You tease me last time.

167
00:15:32,332 --> 00:15:35,321
Well have some tear-gas.

168
00:15:35,566 --> 00:15:37,759
So you'll cry on your wedding day.

169
00:15:52,065 --> 00:15:53,963
Don't exaggerate.

170
00:15:55,599 --> 00:15:56,792
Okay, you win.

171
00:16:02,065 --> 00:16:03,053
Make way.

172
00:16:03,699 --> 00:16:04,596
Let me.

173
00:16:04,733 --> 00:16:06,528
No, you're clumsy.

174
00:16:06,599 --> 00:16:07,792
So much the better.

175
00:16:08,699 --> 00:16:10,289
Let me taste this nice cup of coffee.

176
00:16:11,699 --> 00:16:14,187
Your heart's weak.
Don't drink coffee anymore.

177
00:16:15,033 --> 00:16:17,726
I only meant to fool them.

178
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:19,488
You've fooled me too.

179
00:16:19,666 --> 00:16:20,757
No.

180
00:16:20,966 --> 00:16:23,761
Stop lying, tell me the truth.

181
00:16:23,866 --> 00:16:25,059
Do you love Shirley?

182
00:16:25,966 --> 00:16:29,557
If you don't say it, it means you don't.

183
00:16:29,699 --> 00:16:31,187
No, but...

184
00:16:31,633 --> 00:16:35,326
I still can't make up my mind
after such a long time.

185
00:16:37,699 --> 00:16:38,892
I love her then.

186
00:16:41,966 --> 00:16:45,057
You're not sincere.

187
00:16:45,167 --> 00:16:46,860
Have you finished talking?

188
00:16:47,167 --> 00:16:48,462
Go now, They're pushing.

189
00:16:48,666 --> 00:16:49,859
I'll go then.

190
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:51,091
Bye-bye!

191
00:16:51,699 --> 00:16:54,494
Really heartless, idiot.

192
00:16:55,267 --> 00:16:56,562
Take it off first.

193
00:16:57,066 --> 00:16:58,157
Right.

194
00:16:59,800 --> 00:17:01,698
Remember to collect
the bride at 10 tomorrow.

195
00:17:01,800 --> 00:17:03,198
Wear a necktie.

196
00:17:03,333 --> 00:17:04,923
Thank you. Bye-bye.

197
00:17:07,966 --> 00:17:09,262
Try it at once.

198
00:17:32,599 --> 00:17:33,690
Really beautiful.

199
00:17:38,866 --> 00:17:40,355
The flower on the head is beautiful.

200
00:18:28,200 --> 00:18:29,188
Hsiu!

201
00:18:32,933 --> 00:18:33,831
Don't run.

202
00:18:56,834 --> 00:18:57,731
Hsiu!

203
00:18:58,200 --> 00:18:59,598
Call an ambulance at once!

204
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:07,593
Hsiu...

205
00:19:07,734 --> 00:19:16,633
Shir... Shirley, I...

206
00:19:32,934 --> 00:19:34,331
Hsiu...

207
00:19:53,301 --> 00:19:54,198
What happened...

208
00:20:03,301 --> 00:20:04,198
C.I.D.

209
00:20:58,201 --> 00:20:59,996
Heavenly Father of all men.

210
00:21:00,168 --> 00:21:03,066
We pray especially for those we love

211
00:21:03,134 --> 00:21:04,430
but can't see any more.

212
00:21:04,601 --> 00:21:08,590
May you bless them and shine on them.

213
00:21:08,734 --> 00:21:12,326
May the love, wisdom

214
00:21:12,468 --> 00:21:14,763
and omnipotence,

215
00:21:14,901 --> 00:21:18,299
be demonstrated in them.

216
00:21:18,434 --> 00:21:21,423
We pray in Jesus' name, Amen.

217
00:21:37,535 --> 00:21:39,330
Why are you back from your leave?

218
00:21:39,901 --> 00:21:41,390
There's no point in taking leave now.

219
00:21:41,802 --> 00:21:44,700
Michael, I'm applying for return to duty.

220
00:21:46,134 --> 00:21:48,726
Good. Work may do you good.

221
00:22:56,269 --> 00:23:00,065
Master. I'm in trouble. You must help.

222
00:23:00,169 --> 00:23:01,964
You made things so bad.

223
00:23:02,102 --> 00:23:04,000
Who'd help you?

224
00:23:04,102 --> 00:23:07,397
Here's a potion of American ginseng.

225
00:23:07,501 --> 00:23:08,899
See if it will help.

226
00:23:41,935 --> 00:23:43,231
Don't move. Police.

227
00:23:44,802 --> 00:23:46,393
Yu, handcuff him.

228
00:23:48,402 --> 00:23:49,493
Don't move!

229
00:23:52,968 --> 00:23:54,264
Where's Swatow Hsiung?

230
00:23:54,435 --> 00:23:55,628
I don't know. Miss.

231
00:23:59,269 --> 00:24:00,757
I don't know...

232
00:24:01,735 --> 00:24:02,531
Speak up!

233
00:24:02,636 --> 00:24:03,828
I really don't know.

234
00:24:03,935 --> 00:24:06,231
You're his best friend! Speak up!

235
00:24:06,902 --> 00:24:07,993
Speak up!

236
00:24:11,868 --> 00:24:13,562
Are you going to speak or not?

237
00:24:18,435 --> 00:24:24,334
Maybe these 2 monsters may speak.

238
00:24:24,769 --> 00:24:26,064
Sorry, I don't know anything.

239
00:24:26,135 --> 00:24:27,032
Let's go.

240
00:24:27,302 --> 00:24:28,495
Don't, Mr. Big.

241
00:24:29,235 --> 00:24:30,132
Go over there!

242
00:24:31,536 --> 00:24:33,434
Don't scare madam.

243
00:24:34,302 --> 00:24:35,892
Be smart and speak.

244
00:24:35,968 --> 00:24:36,866
I really don't know.

245
00:24:36,935 --> 00:24:38,731
Don't blame me
if your bottom gets burnt.

246
00:24:38,836 --> 00:24:39,824
Hear that?

247
00:24:39,968 --> 00:24:41,059
I really don't know.

248
00:24:41,169 --> 00:24:43,761
