Speak up!

249
00:24:44,335 --> 00:24:45,323
Take off your pants!

250
00:24:45,736 --> 00:24:47,133
Take off your pants!

251
00:24:47,269 --> 00:24:49,167
You're not speaking? Scald him.

252
00:24:49,269 --> 00:24:50,166
Good.

253
00:24:51,135 --> 00:24:52,431
I enjoy doing it.

254
00:24:53,135 --> 00:24:55,533
You don't care a damn about me.

255
00:24:55,803 --> 00:24:58,598
Speak up!

256
00:24:59,202 --> 00:25:02,794
No?

257
00:25:04,235 --> 00:25:08,429
No?

258
00:25:10,769 --> 00:25:11,962
